{"id":576,"ayahs":[{"number":18,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ","translation":"Behold, [when Our messages are conveyed to one who is bent on denying the truth,] he reflects and meditates [as to how to disprove them] –","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5513.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":20640,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"সে নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/074_018_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20641,"position":2,"arabic":"فَكَّرَ","translation":"চিন্তা করল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_018_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20642,"position":3,"arabic":"وَقَدَّرَ","translation":"এবং সে সিদ্ধান্ত নিল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_018_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":20643,"position":4,"arabic":"١٨","translation":"(১৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":19,"arabic":"فَقُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ","translation":"and thus he destroys himself, the way he meditates:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5514.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":21696,"position":1,"arabic":"فَقُتِلَ","translation":"সে নস্যাৎ তাই হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/074_019_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21697,"position":2,"arabic":"كَيْفَ","translation":"কেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/074_019_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21698,"position":3,"arabic":"قَدَّرَ","translation":"সে সিদ্ধান্ত নিল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_019_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":21699,"position":4,"arabic":"١٩","translation":"(১৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":20,"arabic":"ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَيْفَ قَدَّرَ","translation":"yea, he destroys himself, the way he meditates!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5515.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":22871,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"আবারও","audioUrl":"wbw/074_020_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22872,"position":2,"arabic":"قُتِلَ","translation":"মার পড়ল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_020_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22873,"position":3,"arabic":"كَيْفَ","translation":"কেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/074_020_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22874,"position":4,"arabic":"قَدَّرَ","translation":"সিদ্ধান্ত নিল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_020_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22875,"position":5,"arabic":"٢٠","translation":"(২০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":21,"arabic":"ثُمَّ نَظَرَ","translation":"and then he looks [around for new arguments],","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5516.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":23959,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/074_021_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23960,"position":2,"arabic":"نَظَرَ","translation":"সে তাকাল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_021_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23961,"position":3,"arabic":"٢١","translation":"(২১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":22,"arabic":"ثُمَّ عَبَسَ وَبَسَرَ","translation":"and then he frowns and glares,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5517.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":24998,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/074_022_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24999,"position":2,"arabic":"عَبَسَ","translation":"কপাল কুচড়াল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_022_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25000,"position":3,"arabic":"وَبَسَرَ","translation":"ও মুখ বাঁকাল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_022_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25001,"position":4,"arabic":"٢٢","translation":"(২২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":23,"arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدْبَرَ وَٱسْتَكْبَرَ","translation":"and in the end he turns his back [on Our message], and glories in his arrogance,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5518.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":26001,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/074_023_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26002,"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْبَرَ","translation":"সে ফিরল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_023_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26003,"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱسْتَكْبَرَ","translation":"এবং অহংকার করল","audioUrl":"wbw/074_023_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26004,"position":4,"arabic":"٢٣","translation":"(২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":24,"arabic":"فَقَالَ إِنْ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا سِحْرٌۭ يُؤْثَرُ","translation":"and says, \"All this is mere spellbinding eloquence handed down [from olden times]!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5519.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":27084,"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَالَ","translation":"সে বলল অতঃপর","audioUrl":"wbw/074_024_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27085,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنْ","translation":"\"নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/074_024_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27086,"position":3,"arabic":"هَـٰذَآ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/074_024_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27087,"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/074_024_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27088,"position":5,"arabic":"سِحْرٌۭ","translation":"জাদু","audioUrl":"wbw/074_024_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27089,"position":6,"arabic":"يُؤْثَرُ","translation":"চলে আসা","audioUrl":"wbw/074_024_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27090,"position":7,"arabic":"٢٤","translation":"(২৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":25,"arabic":"إِنْ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا قَوْلُ ٱلْبَشَرِ","translation":"This is nothing but the word of mortal man!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5520.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":28095,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنْ","translation":"নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/074_025_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28096,"position":2,"arabic":"هَـٰذَآ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/074_025_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28097,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/074_025_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28098,"position":4,"arabic":"قَوْلُ","translation":"কথা","audioUrl":"wbw/074_025_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28099,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْبَشَرِ","translation":"মানুুষের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/074_025_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28100,"position":6,"arabic":"٢٥","translation":"(২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":26,"arabic":"سَأُصْلِيهِ سَقَرَ","translation":"[Hence,] I shall cause him to endure hell-fire [in the life to come]!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5521.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":29050,"position":1,"arabic":"سَأُصْلِيهِ","translation":"তাকে প্রবেশ আমি শীঘ্রই করাবো","audioUrl":"wbw/074_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29051,"position":2,"arabic":"سَقَرَ","translation":"দোযখে","audioUrl":"wbw/074_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29052,"position":3,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا سَقَرُ","translation":"And what could make thee conceive what hell-fire is?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5522.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":29862,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"এবং কি","audioUrl":"wbw/074_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29863,"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","translation":"তুমি জান","audioUrl":"wbw/074_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29864,"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"কি সেই","audioUrl":"wbw/074_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29865,"position":4,"arabic":"سَقَرُ","translation":"দোযখ","audioUrl":"wbw/074_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29866,"position":5,"arabic":"٢٧","translation":"(২৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":28,"arabic":"لَا تُبْقِى وَلَا تَذَرُ","translation":"It does not allow to live, and neither leaves [to die],","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5523.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":31002,"position":1,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/074_028_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31003,"position":2,"arabic":"تُبْقِى","translation":"বাকী রাখে","audioUrl":"wbw/074_028_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31004,"position":3,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/074_028_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31005,"position":4,"arabic":"تَذَرُ","translation":"ছেড়ে দেয়","audioUrl":"wbw/074_028_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31006,"position":5,"arabic":"٢٨","translation":"(২৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":29,"arabic":"لَوَّاحَةٌۭ لِّلْبَشَرِ","translation":"making [all truth] visible to mortal man.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5524.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":31982,"position":1,"arabic":"لَوَّاحَةٌۭ","translation":"ঝলসে দেয়","audioUrl":"wbw/074_029_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31983,"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلْبَشَرِ","translation":"চামড়াকে","audioUrl":"wbw/074_029_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31984,"position":3,"arabic":"٢٩","translation":"(২৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":30,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا تِسْعَةَ عَشَرَ","translation":"Over it are nineteen [powers].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5525.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":32862,"position":1,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","translation":"তার উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/074_030_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32863,"position":2,"arabic":"تِسْعَةَ","translation":"উনিশ","audioUrl":"wbw/074_030_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32864,"position":3,"arabic":"عَشَرَ","translation":"(প্রহরী)","audioUrl":"wbw/074_030_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32865,"position":4,"arabic":"٣٠","translation":"(৩০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":31,"arabic":"وَمَا جَعَلْنَآ أَصْحَٰبَ ٱلنَّارِ إِلَّا مَلَٰٓئِكَةًۭ ۙ وَمَا جَعَلْنَا عِدَّتَهُمْ إِلَّا فِتْنَةًۭ لِّلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لِيَسْتَيْقِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُوا۟ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ وَيَزْدَادَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ إِيمَٰنًۭا ۙ وَلَا يَرْتَابَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُوا۟ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ وَٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ ۙ وَلِيَقُولَ ٱلَّذِينَ فِى قُلُوبِهِم مَّرَضٌۭ وَٱلْكَٰفِرُونَ مَاذَآ أَرَادَ ٱللَّهُ بِهَٰذَا مَثَلًۭا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يُضِلُّ ٱللَّهُ مَن يَشَآءُ وَيَهْدِى مَن يَشَآءُ ۚ وَمَا يَعْلَمُ جُنُودَ رَبِّكَ إِلَّا هُوَ ۚ وَمَا هِىَ إِلَّا ذِكْرَىٰ لِلْبَشَرِ","translation":"For We have caused none but angelic powers to lord over the fire [of hell]; and We have not caused their number to be aught but a trial for those who are bent on denying the truth - to the end that they who have been granted revelation aforetime might be convinced [of the truth of this divine writ]; and that they who have attained to faith [in it] might grow yet more firm in their faith; and that [both] they who have been granted the earlier revelation and they who believe [in this one] might be freed of all doubt; and that they in whose hearts is disease and the who deny the truth outright might ask, \"What does [your] God mean by this parable?\" In this way God lets go astray him that wills [to go astray], and guides aright him that wills [to be guided]. And none can comprehend thy Sustainers forces save Him alone: and all this is but a reminder to mortal man.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5526.mp3","surahId":74,"words":[{"id":33661,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/074_031_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33662,"position":2,"arabic":"جَعَلْنَآ","translation":"আমরা বানিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/074_031_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33663,"position":3,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبَ","translation":"কর্মচারীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/074_031_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33664,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","translation":"দোযখের","audioUrl":"wbw/074_031_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33665,"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/074_031_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33666,"position":6,"arabic":"مَلَـٰٓئِكَةًۭ ۙ","translation":"ফেরেশতাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/074_031_006.mp3","cha